\nc<Reporter>"Then, in celebration of the success of 'Storming into the
Succubus First Industry!'... Cheers!"

\nc<Saki>"Cheers~ (Since I'm here, I've got to eat lots of delicious
food! I deserve it after all!)"

\nc<Reporter>"Saki-chan, is this really your first time on a show? You
were so good, it surprised me."

\nc<Saki>"N-no, I'm still...[bustMsgExp[1, 2]](Well, you guys were
better at sexual harassment... It seemed to be the concept
of the show, so I guess I should just let it slide, right?)"
\nc<Reporter>"Come on, drink up. This is quite a good liquor."

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>"(I don't have good memories with alcohol, but one drink
should be fine...) Uh, is this whiskey? It's quite strong."
\nc<Reporter>"Ah, you don't have to force yourself to drink."

\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>"Ahaha, thank you. Then I'll have a non-alcoholic...(They're
not forcing me to drink. Well, it's the times we live in!
Maybe everyone is actually nice!)"
